{
  "stem": "2581.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her full name was Feigan Naches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think the last name was [INAUDIBLE], because I think it was she had married-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it never came up when I was a child what the last name was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was Feigan Naches.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everyone in the city, in the town knew Feigan Naches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was selling fruits and vegetables on the market.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember wintertime, when it was cold, and my father-- you know, we were tailors-- he was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to send out a worker with a pot with hot coal, you know, those tailor-- that you put in an iron.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she would put it underneath her big skirt and that would keep her warm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she was a pious, learned, decent woman, proud woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was tall in posture, and she carried herself that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the synagogue, she was what was called a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She prayed in the large synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a woman with-- at that time, many, many women couldn't read Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was this woman that would read and they would repeat, and she was-- she did that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she, on Saturday, she would sit all day over-- over the Seder, and mostly in the afternoon, but the [NON-ENGLISH], and read it aloud to whoever passed by could hear.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And across from where she lived, there was this movie house, and they opened the movie house at 4:30.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Jewish people started to go to the movie house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were some people that were spiteful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Most Jews wouldn't do that, but there were people that didn't believe in God, that were communist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was very modern at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They wanted just to be spiteful.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
